$$  Life on the Internet punishes slow-loading web pages. The key to fast   $$
$$     downloads and attractive sites is to optimize your graphics and      $$
$$  animations with Ulead SmartSaver Pro. SmartSaver Pro will drastically   $$
$$ cut the weight out of web graphics, sometimes by as much as two-thirds.  $$
$$  Ulead SmartSaver Pro is literally all you need to get your graphics     $$
$$  ready for the web. Besides powerful optimization routines, SmartSaver   $$
$$  also features image slicing, HTML map tags, flexible batch processing,  $$
$$     one click switching between GIF, JPG, and PNG files, background      $$
$$   blending, easy JavaScript Rollovers and more. Ulead SmartSaver Pro     $$
$$    works as a stand alone or it can be installed right inside your       $$
$$                          favorite image editor.                          $$
